    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "39. If ye were Abraham's children, ye would do the works of Abraham—He had just said He \"knew they were Abraham's children,\" that is, according to the flesh; but the children of his faith and holiness they were not, but the reverse.",
